
LAB08 QUESTION:

1.	Implement the following dialogues using TCP sockets:	
a.	Client to Authentication Server : ID of client ║ Password ║ Request
(Request : HTTP request for a file)	
b.	Authentication Server verifies the password, 
(i)	if correct, then the request is forwarded to the Service Providing Server by the Authentication Server
(ii)	else, send back an authentication fail message to the client 

c.	Service Providing Server sends back the file to the Authentication Server which in turn sends it back to the Client. (Reply in HTTP packet format)	
d.	Finally display the content in the file at the Client side	


Note: The file content should be individual student’s details like Reg. no, Name, Address, Area of Interest for the Final Year Project.
